title: #92Noon! Nordo in for PA! Heath/Russo/Reuter/Micheletti/Hayes/Berhow
description: Nordo is in for PA, he is joined at the beginning of the show by head coach of Minnesota United, Adrian Heath. The Athletic's and elite hockey mind, Michael Russo, and also from The Athletic, MLS writer Jeff Reuter. Pat Micheletti's triumphant in studio appearance. The Athletic's Dan Hayes on baseball's imminent return and senior editor of Golf.com, Jeff Berhow.
